  <name>OpenWispr</name>
  <summary>Desktop dictation application using OpenAI Whisper</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      OpenWispr is a desktop dictation application that uses OpenAI Whisper for 
      speech-to-text transcription. It supports both local (privacy-focused) and 
      cloud (OpenAI API) processing modes.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Global hotkey activation</li>
      <li>Local and cloud transcription modes</li>
      <li>Multiple language support</li>
      <li>Always-on-top dictation interface</li>
      <li>Clipboard integration</li>
      <li>Transcription history</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
